# Frontend Design

For UI changes in this project, read and follow `.agents/skills/frontend-design/SKILL.md` before writing code.

Use it when the user asks to build, style, redesign, or beautify pages, components, or layouts.

Key points:
- Pick a bold, intentional aesthetic direction
- Use distinctive typography and cohesive color
- Add motion and spatial composition with purpose
- Avoid generic fonts (Inter, Arial) and clichéd purple-gradient layouts
